targets.query: SELECT sum(loggedAgents)*10000/$__interval_ms FROM aggregated.host_agents WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval)
SELECT mean("cpu_usage") FROM "procstat" WHERE process_name = 'agentserver' and $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host
SELECT sum("totalPackets")*100/(3*$__interval_ms) FROM "rtpprocessor.voice" WHERE $timeFilter  GROUP BY  time($interval)
SELECT mean("cpu_usage") FROM "procstat" WHERE process_name = 'rtpprocessor' and $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host
SELECT sum(activeCalls)*10000/$__interval_ms  FROM "sipprocessor.trunk" WHERE $timeFilter  GROUP BY time($__interval)
SELECT mean("cpu_usage") FROM "procstat" WHERE process_name = 'sipprocessor' and $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host
SELECT (sum(activeVoiceInteractions)+sum(activeChatInteractions))*10000/$__interval_ms FROM aggregated.host_scenario WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval)
SELECT mean("cpu_usage") FROM "procstat" WHERE process_name = 'scenarioengine' and $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host
SELECT difference(sum(totalVoiceInteractions))/6 FROM scenarioengine WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1m)

targets.query: select sum(activeCalls)*10000/($__interval_ms) from dialer where $timeFilter and activeCalls > 0  group by time($__interval),hostname
SELECT mean("cpu_usage") FROM "procstat" WHERE process_name = 'dialer' and $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host
SELECT mean("cpu_usage") FROM "procstat" WHERE process_name = 'pwrdialer' and $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host
SELECT mean("cpu_usage") FROM "procstat" WHERE pidfile = '/var/run/servicepattern/webagentdesktop.pid' and $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval*3), host
SELECT mean("cpu_usage") FROM "procstat" WHERE pidfile = '/var/run/servicepattern/webportal.pid' and $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval*3), host
SELECT mean("cpu_usage") FROM "procstat" WHERE process_name = 'mongod' and $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval*3), exe, host
SELECT mean("cpu_usage") FROM "procstat" WHERE process_name = 'mysqld' and $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval*3), exe, host
SELECT mean("used_percent") FROM "disk" WHERE "host" =~ /^$mongo$/ AND "path" !~ /.*boot.*|.*storage.*/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY path, host, time($__interval) fill(null)
